General description 
In this prospective, multicentre cohort performed between August 2020 and March 2022, we recruited hospital employees from ten acute/nonacute healthcare networks in Eastern/Northern Switzerland. We determined immune status in September 2021 based on serology and previous SARS-CoV-2 infections/vaccinations: Group N (no immunity); Group V (twice vaccinated, uninfected); Group I (infected, unvaccinated); Group H (hybrid: infected and ≥1 vaccination). The dataset is consisting of two files, one describing vaccination and infection events for all healthworkers, and the secone one describing the symptoms for the healthworkers who tested positive for SARS-CoV-2.

Data in the file "TimeToInfection.csv" is organised in time intervals, from day_interval_start to day_interval_stop. Missing data is shown as "" for not indicated. It contains 16 columns:
ID Unique Identifier, same in both files
group Vaccination group: "N" (no immunity), "V" (twice vaccinated, uninfected), "I" (infected, unvaccinated), "H" (hybrid: infected and ≥1 vaccination)
age age in years, 
sex "female", "male" (or "" for not indicated)	
BMI categorical, ">30" or "<30"	
patient_contact	1=yes, 0=no 
using_FFP2_mask 1=yes, 0=no 
negative_swab 1=yes, 0=no 
booster 1=yes, 0=no (or "" for not indicated)	
positive_household 1=yes, 0=no	
months_since_immunisation continuous, in months	
time_dose1_to_dose_2 continuous, in months
vaccinetype Categorical, "Moderna" or "Pfizer/BioNTech" (or "" for not indicated)	
day_interval_start day since start of study when the interval starts
day_interval_stop day since start of study when the interval stops	
infection_event 1=yes, 0=no

Data in the file "Symptoms.csv" is organised per infected health care worker. Each worker is only indicated once. It contains 11 columns:
ID Unique Identifier, same in both files
group Vaccination group: "N" (no immunity), "V" (twice vaccinated, uninfected), "I" (infected, unvaccinated), "H" (hybrid: infected and ≥1 vaccination)
age age in years, 
sex "female", "male" (or "" for not indicated)	
BMI categorical, ">30" or "<30"	
comorbidity 1=yes, 0=no	
using_FFP2_mask 1=yes, 0=no	
months_until_reinfection time until next infection	
variant	categorical, delta or omicron (or "" for not indicated)	
booster_over7_days_before	
symptom_number Number of symptoms during the infection
